---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>Learn more about the platform and the lecturer behind it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="platform-section">
        <span class="badge">About the Platform</span>
        <h2>OET Learning Platform</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          A structured digital learning platform designed specifically for healthcare professionals
          preparing for the Occupational English Test (OET). Our mission is to make English
          language learning accessible, practical, and relevant to medical contexts.
        </p>

        <div class="card-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <span class="card-icon">🎯</span>
            <h3>Who It's For</h3>
            <p>
              Healthcare professionals including doctors, nurses, pharmacists, dentists, and
              allied health workers who need to prove their English proficiency.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <span class="card-icon">💡</span>
            <h3>Why It Exists</h3>
            <p>
              Traditional OET resources often lack medical specificity. This platform bridges
              that gap with contextually relevant materials and AI-assisted practice.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <span class="card-icon">📚</span>
            <h3>Learning Approach</h3>
            <p>
              We use a flipped classroom model where you learn concepts at home through modules
              and practice skills via AI chatbot sessions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features-box">
          <h3>What You'll Find Here</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Structured Modules</strong> — Progressive learning from foundations to mastery</li>
            <li><strong>AI-Assisted Practice</strong> — Chatbot-powered role-play and speaking practice</li>
            <li><strong>Real Medical Contexts</strong> — Vocabulary, scenarios, and dialogues from healthcare settings</li>
            <li><strong>Immediate Feedback</strong> — AI-powered evaluation of your speaking and writing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="lecturer-section">
        <span class="badge">About the Lecturer</span>

        <div class="lecturer-card">
          <div class="lecturer-header">
            <div class="avatar">
              <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
                <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="32" fill="#2563eb"/>
                <circle cx="32" cy="26" r="12" fill="#93c5fd"/>
                <path d="M12 56C12 44.954 20.954 36 32 36C43.046 36 52 44.954 52 56" fill="#93c5fd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="lecturer-name">Emilius German</h3>
              <p class="lecturer-role">Academic & Lecturer — President University</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            <strong>Emilius German</strong> is an academic and lecturer specializing in English
            Language Education with a focus on Educational Technology (EdTech). He is actively
            engaged in teaching, research, and developing digital-based learning innovations.
          </p>
          <p>
            As an academic adapting to the evolving educational landscape, Emilius emphasizes
            enhancing learning quality through technology, particularly in English language
            education within the digital era.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-grid">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Areas of Expertise</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>English Language Education</li>
              <li>Educational Technology (EdTech)</li>
              <li>Applied Linguistics</li>
              <li>Curriculum Development</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Research Interests</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Online learning</li>
              <li>Self-regulated learning</li>
              <li>Technology integration in language learning</li>
              <li>Development of teaching methods and learning media</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Academic Profile</h3>
          <p>
            Emilius German maintains an <strong>applied research orientation</strong>, focusing on
            practical solutions in education. His research explores how technology can improve
            learning effectiveness within the Indonesian educational context.
          </p>
          <p>
            He is currently pursuing a <strong>Doctoral (Ph.D.) degree in Educational Technology</strong>,
            demonstrating his commitment to advancing expertise in the field.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Scholarly Characteristics</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Interdisciplinary — bridging education, technology, and language</li>
            <li>Practice-oriented and implementation-focused</li>
            <li>Responsive to digital learning developments</li>
            <li>Committed to improving learning quality</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card highlight">
          <h3>Summary</h3>
          <p>
            Emilius German is an academic dedicated to advancing technology-enhanced English language
            learning. With a practical and context-relevant approach, he continues to contribute to
            developing effective, adaptive, and impactful learning innovations in modern education.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Developed by <a href="https://hijrahassalam.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hijrahassalam.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-20);
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    background: var(--color-primary-50);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 100px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  /* Platform Section */
  .platform-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-16);
  }

  .platform-section h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    padding: var(--space-5);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .card p,
  .card li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card li {
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .card li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 8px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .features-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-50), var(--color-surface));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary-100);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .features-box h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .features-box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .features-box li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    position: relative;
  }

  .features-box li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Divider */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    margin: var(--space-12) 0;
  }

  /* Lecturer Section */
  .lecturer-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .lecturer-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .lecturer-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-5);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  .avatar {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .lecturer-name {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .lecturer-role {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .lecturer-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .lecturer-card p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .highlight {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .footer p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .footer a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .footer a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .lecturer-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>